726892f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 203rd Avenue
726892f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., at the S.W. corner of 203rd Street (left, not
shown), showing in a set of three views the Peter Van Siclen house
house from 1873-1896. J. Carpenter was the owner in 1860.
1922.
View 2: May 1923.
View 3: April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAr BE REPRODUCED.
